  Kernel::ComputeArea_2  


A model for this must provide:
 

    
          Kernel ::FT  

         
          
             
    fo.operator() (     
      Kernel::Point_2  p,  Kernel::Point_2  q,  Kernel::Point_2  r)     
                
    returns the signed  area  of the triangle defined by the points  p ,
        q  and  r .
                 
          Kernel ::FT  

         
          
         
    fo.operator() (   Kernel :: Iso_rectangle_2  r)
         
                
    returns the  area  of  r .
                 
          Kernel ::FT  

         
          
         
    fo.operator() (   Kernel::Triangle_2  t)
         
                
    returns the signed  area  of  t .
            

  Refines  AdaptableFunctor  (with one argument)
 

  See Also   CGAL::Iso_rectangle_2 &lt; Kernel &gt;    CGAL::Triangle_2 &lt; Kernel &gt;   

